#: ../messaging/applications.rst:190
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr ""
"如何運作"

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:191
msgid "The IoTF service extends the MQTT 3.1.1 specification to provide support for shared subscriptions. Shared subscription can provide simple load balancing functionality for applications. A shared subscription might be needed if a back-end enterprise application can not keep up with the number of messages being published to a specific topic space. For example if many devices were publishing messages that are being processed by a single application. It might be helpful to leverage the load balancing capability of a shared subscription. IoTF shared subscription support is limited to non-durable subscriptions only."
msgstr ""
"IoTF 服務延伸了 MQTT 3.1.1 規格，以支援分擔訂閱。分擔訂閱可為應用程式提供簡單的負載平衡功能。如果後端企業應用程式無法跟上要發佈至特定主題空間的訊息數，則可能需要分擔訂閱。例如，如果有多個裝置發佈的訊息都是由單一應用程式所處理。運用分擔訂閱的負載平衡功能，可能會有所幫助。IoTF 分擔訂閱支援僅限於不可延續的訂閱。"

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:199
msgid "A simple example of an auto-scaling application:"
msgstr ""
"自動調整大小應用程式的簡單範例："

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:201
msgid "client 1 connects as A:abc123:myApplication and subscribes to all device events client 1 will receive 100% of the device events published"
msgstr ""
"用戶端 1 以 A:abc123:myApplication 連接並訂閱所有裝置事件，用戶端 1 會收到 100% 發佈的裝置事件"

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:203
msgid "client 2 connects as A:abc123:myApplication and subscribes to all device events now, client 1 and client 2 will share all of the events published between them. that is the load is now shared between client 1 and client 2."
msgstr ""
"用戶端 2 以 A:abc123:myApplication 連接且現在訂閱所有裝置事件，用戶端 1 與用戶端 2 即會分擔在它們之間發佈的所有事件。也就是說，目前在用戶端 1 與用戶端 2 之間會分擔負載。"

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:206
msgid "client 3 connects as A:abc123:myApplication and subscribes to all device events now, instance 1, 2 and 3 will process the events shared amongst all three instances"
msgstr ""
"用戶端 3 以 A:abc123:myApplication 連接且現在訂閱所有裝置事件，實例 1、2 及 3 將會處理在這三個實例之間分擔的事件"

#: ../messaging/applications.rst:208
msgid "clients 2 and 3 unsubscribe from all device events now, although instance 2 and 3 are still connected to the service, instance 1 will be receiving  all device events published"
msgstr ""
"用戶端 2 及 3 現在取消訂閱所有裝置事件，雖然實例 2 及 3 仍然連接至服務，但實例 1 會接收所有發佈的裝置事件"

